---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Grade 316 Marine Stainless Steel Wire Pegs"
  description="Grade 316 marine stainless steel wire pegs are the toughest option — perfect for coastal homes, boats, and harsh outdoor conditions. Will never rust."
>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-4">Grade 316 · Marine Grade</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-800 leading-tight mb-6">Marine Grade Stainless Steel Wire Pegs</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">The ultimate wire peg. Built for coastal Australia, boats, and anyone who refuses to compromise on quality.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-6">Product specs</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <p class="text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Grade</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-800">316 Marine Stainless Steel</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <p class="text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Wire Diameter</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-800">1.7mm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <p class="text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Length</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-800">5.8cm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <p class="text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Pack Sizes</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-800">24, 36 or 50 pegs</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">Is Grade 316 right for you?</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Grade 316 is the same steel used on boats and in marine construction. It contains molybdenum — an element that gives it exceptional resistance to salt, chlorine, and harsh weather.</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">If you live near the coast, on a boat, or simply want the absolute best peg money can buy — Grade 316 is the one. Leave them outside permanently, in any conditions, and they will not rust.</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">One customer even described them as "cocky proof" after local cockatoos gave up trying to steal them off the line.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">Best for</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Coastal homes and marine environments</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Leaving pegs outside permanently in any conditions</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Boats and waterfront properties</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Anyone who wants the absolute best</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span> Harsh weather and high salt environments</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-stone-800 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Tip for coastal use</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Store your Grade 316 pegs in a bucket with holes in the bottom so rainwater can rinse away any salt buildup. This keeps them looking their best for decades.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="bg-stone-800 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-stone-700 transition-colors text-lg">Buy Grade 316 Pegs at Biome →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex gap-4">
      <a href="/products/grade-201" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 hover:text-stone-900 underline underline-offset-4">← View Grade 201</a>
      <a href="/products/grade-304" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 hover:text-stone-900 underline underline-offset-4">← View Grade 304</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>